text: The 1946 New Mexico gubernatorial election took place on November 5, 1946, in order to elect the Governor of New Mexico. Incumbent Democrat John J. Dempsey was term-limited, and could not run for reelection to a third consecutive term. ==General election== ===Results=== ==References== gubernatorial 1946 New Mexico Category:November 1946 events
title: 1946 New Mexico gubernatorial election
